review
It lets you:
• Improve code quality
• Learn from others and improve software engineering skills


You can use these templates to give clear and collaborative feedback:

✓ I think it'd be better if we...
✓ This solution wouldn't work because...
✓ Great catch! Just one small suggestion…

✓ Let’s consider refactoring this because...
✓ Do we have a test covering this scenario?
✓ This part is hard to follow, so could you please...

✓ Let’s address this now to avoid technical debt later.
✓ Let’s align this with our team’s standards for consistency.
✓ I noticed a potential performance issue here, so maybe we can...


Remember, code review is about teamwork, not fighting.
And good code reviews shouldn't slow down the development process.
